<item>
            <title>[SOLR-4976] info stream doesn&apos;t work with merged segment warmer</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-4976</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In SolrIndexConfig, constructing the merged segment warmer takes an InfoStream, but InfoStream.NO_OUTPUT is hardcoded.  Instead, the info stream should be constructed in SolrIndexConfig, instead of SolrIndexWriter where it is now, so that it can be used for the warmer.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
